These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-1::.
There 4 different types of food: orange, lemon, tomato, strawberry
1. the person eating orange is on the far left##1
2. the person eating lemon is on the left or right of the person eating orange##3
3. the person eating lemon is on the left or right of the person eating tomato##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2     |  3   |   4    |
| Food   | orange | lemon | tomato | strawberry |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, soy-milk, lemonade, almond-milk
1. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
2. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
3. the person drinking lemonade is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | mirinda | almond-milk | lemonade |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: reading, cooking, traveling, dancing
1. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
2. the person who's hobby is reading is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby   | reading | traveling | cooking | dancing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, family, documentary, fantasy
1. the person watching documentary movies is on the far right##1
2. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the person watching fantasy movies##1
3. the person watching adventure movies is on the left or right of the person watching fantasy movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |  4  |
| Movie-Genre   | family | adventure | fantasy | documentary |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-5::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: soccer, volleyball, baseball, rowing
1. the person who's sport is soccer is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
3. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |    2    |  3   |     4      |
| Sport   | rowing | baseball | volleyball | soccer |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-6::.
