.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-10::.
There 4 different types of food: potato, nectarine, apricot, pineapple
1. the person eating nectarine is on the right of the person eating pineapple##1
2. the person eating nectarine is between the person eating potato and the person eating pineapple##2
3. the person eating potato is on the left or right of the person eating apricot##3
4. the person eating potato is on the left or right of the person eating apricot##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2     |    3    |    4    |
| Food   | pineapple | nectarine | potato | apricot |

